    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six, exhibiting strong compression and a crisp VANOS engagement. Meticulously maintained, the subframe has been reinforced to handle the lateral G-forces provided by the upgraded coilover suspension. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, while the limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and new rod bearings for preventative peace of mind. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved performance machine, while the chassis remains rigid and responsive. An ideal candidate for the enthusiast seeking a mechanically sound, high-revving icon.",
